      <title>波音资本最快将于周一筹集逾 150 亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-28/boeing-capital-raise-over-15-billion-may-come-as-soon-as-monday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司计划最早于周一筹集超过 150 亿美元的资金，此举将帮助这家陷入困境的飞机制造商提高流动性。凯特·达菲在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-28/boeing-capital-raise-over-15-billion-may-come-as-soon-as-monday</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 10:29:12 GMT</pubDate>
